org.dessertj.resolve

Class ClassPackage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dessertj.resolve.ClassPackage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClassRoot, VersionRoot

    public class ClassPackage
extends Object
    A ClassEntry represents a single package within one classes directory or .jar file. It's either linked to the parent ClassPackage it belongs to or it is a ClassRoot itself. It maintains a probably empty list of all its subpackages and classes it contains directly. If there is another package with the same name in some other classes directory or .jar file within the ClassResolver scope it has a reference to a list of all such packages.
